10
11
granted to any credit union pursuant to subsection C of this section
11
12
and may suspend or revoke such authority if it finds that the credit
12
13
union has failed to comply with federal or state laws or regulations
13
14
applicable to virtual currency custody services or any existing
14
15
conditions imposed by the Department or if the services are
15
